We are looking for a highly skilled senior network and server administrator who is naturally
passionate about IT to join our growing team.

-Manage network components: Windows Servers, Active Directory, Exchange, Office 365
server backups, licensing network infrastructures and devices (firewalls and switches),
virtualization (ESXi), Veeam;
-You will jointly be responsible for the support and management of networks ranging from
10-100+ servers and end-user;
-Provide high-quality support to our customers and take ownership of incidents and requests
until resolution;
-In team collaboration, planning, and managing infrastructures and migrations;
-Supporting Level 1 and 2 teams with advanced technical issues and providing guidance and
coaching;
-Availability to occasionally work evenings and weekends for emergencies, with
compensation.

