-Previous experience in configuring, operating, and managing networks, servers, storage
equipment of various brands, and a VMware environment;
-Knowledge of security-related systems and applications such as firewalls, intrusion detection
systems, virtual private networks (VPNs), and associated network and protocols and
concepts;
-Possess an interest in and ability to learn new and emerging technologies.

